      "type": "html",
      "text": " An Address class. This could be a simple symbolic tag. More usefully, it's a slash delimited path; I've built a variant in which it was an arbitrarily dimensional closed surface indexing into a geometric database.",
      "id": "ffe44d16b912ad9b93179297db30a897"
